latestIgtvVideos.title: Kay Beauty - Pure Bloom -  Tutorial 🥰
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey Insta fam ♥️

Hope you like this 🥰 Please read until the end ... also would appreciate if you can tag @kaybykatrina

⚜ I got this on Nykaa for Rs 1199/-
⚜ This is made in China

My review on the Kay Beauty Pure Bloom eye shadow palette ?
⚜ The eye shadows are pigmented and have a velvet feel to it. 
⚜ Fall out is minimal 
⚜ Takes a minimum 2  coats to get
 " real" color.
⚜ Most shades in this palette are warm toned - except 1 cool tone shade.
⚜ The darkest shadow in the palette is not dark enough.  If it was so the palette would gave been more versatile.
⚜ The foiled gold shadow in the palette is stunning.

Would you buy this for Rs 1199?
Would love to know your thoughts 😊
